# Verilock Notary — Docker ignore list
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Files listed here are EXCLUDED from the Docker build context.
# Smaller context = faster builds. More importantly: secrets never reach
# the Docker daemon or get baked into image layers.

# ── SECRETS — never send to Docker ───────────────────────────────────────────
# These contain private keys and tokens. They must never appear in an image layer.
.env
data/
data/notary.key
data/agent.key
data/audit.db
data/backups/

# ── BUILD ARTIFACTS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Go build cache and compiled binaries — the Dockerfile builds these fresh.
bin/
*.exe
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# ── TEST FILES ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Test files are not needed in the production image.
*_test.go
testdata/

# ── DEVELOPMENT FILES ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Local development configs, IDE settings, editor artifacts.
.git/
.gitignore
.github/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── LOGS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
logs/
*.log

# ── DOCUMENTATION ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Docs are not needed in the runtime image.
docs/
*.md
README*
CHANGELOG*
LICENSE*

# ── OTHER SERVICES ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The contracts and SDK are separate — not part of the Go build.
../contracts/
../sdk/